annotations.OOPVerbTenseAnnotation: Verb tenses. past: VBD,VBN present: VB,VBP,VBZ future: MD progressive: VBG infinitive: TO

annotations.OOPAdjectiveCategoriesAnnotation: Good-Better-Best. JJ, JJR, JJS: descriptive, comparative, superlative.

annotations.OOPAdverbCategoriesAnnotation: Fast-Faster-Fasest. RB, RBR, RBS: descriptive, comparative, superlative.

annotations.OOPSVOAnnotation: CoreNLP dependency parse subject-verb-object-indirectObject-auxVerb: nsubj, root, obj, iobj. https://universaldependencies.org/en/dep/

annotations.OOPHowAnnotation: Constituency Parse: SBARQ, WHNP || WHADVP, how. https://gist.github.com/nlothian/9240750

annotations.OOPPeopleAnnotation: CoreNLP NER mentions: I, PERSON minus PRP, PRP$, stray NNP/NNPS; coref

annotations.OOPDatesAnnotation: CoreNLP NER mentions: DATE or TIME

annotations.OOPNounHypernymsAnnotation: Wordnet most likely hypernym based on hyponym match against all nouns.

annotations.OOPWikipediaPageviewTopicsAnnotation: Wikipedia pageviews for the past month (https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/metrics/pageviews/per-article/en.wikipedia.org/all-access/all-agents/Shakespeare) for Topics (NNP,NNPS).

annotations.OOPActorsAnnotation: OOPPeopleAnnotation with sentiment, quotes, coref, and universal dependencies nsubj, nmod:poss, advmod, amod (http://universaldependencies.org/docsv1/en/dep/index.html).
